1
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:39,280
Thank you, Ancestor.

2
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:29,040
Yuyao.

3
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,079
Yuyao.

4
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:36,640
Yuyao.

5
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,900
At least you have some conscience

6
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:42,579
to remember me in your dreams.

7
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,400
Xiao Ai.

8
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,720
Ai.

9
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:07,970
It's not the weekend today.

10
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:10,570
This wretched girl sleeps even more than I do.

11
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,450
It went through.

12
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:21,560
Hello.

13
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:22,160
Hello.

14
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,280
Boss.

15
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,320
Here's the thing.

16
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,050
I'd like to ask for a day off.

17
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:29,680
I called you yesterday but couldn't reach you.

18
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,410
And you didn't reply on WeChat.

19
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,420
My boyfriend came to Tianchi.

20
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,840
It's his first time here.

21
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,600
I want to show him around.

22
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:37,940
You silly girl!

23
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,079
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

24
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:42,040
Have a good time with your boyfriend.

25
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:44,100
I'll treat you two to dinner tonight.

26
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:45,960
Thank you, boss.

27
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,960
Thank you on behalf of my boyfriend.

28
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,640
Great!

29
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,250
How is it?

30
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,520
Have a bite too.

31
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,320
Sinian.

32
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:51,720
Sinian.

33
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,000
Lu Sinian.

34
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,200
Aren't you a Virgo in this life?

35
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,160
How can you be so sloppy?

36
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,060
I must hit the road,

37
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:31,840
so I'll take my leave.

38
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:42,800
Mr. Lu.

39
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:53,400
Sorry,

40
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:56,800
the number you dialed cannot be reached at the moment.

41
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,240
Sorry,

42
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:03,520
the number you dialed cannot be reached at the moment.

43
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:04,850
Please try again later.

44
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:17,840
Sinian.

45
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,560
Sinian.

46
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,600
Lu Sinian.

47
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,480
But didn't we agree

48
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:39,280
to return to Xinjiang after graduation?

49
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,880
That was what we said before.

50
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,600
I spent my four years of college in Beijing.

51
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:45,240
My friends and connections aren't in Xinjiang.

52
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,040
Let me ask you.

53
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:48,080
Are you asking me to come back and start from scratch?

54
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,880
What do you mean, 'start from scratch'?

55
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:51,360
How is it starting from scratch?

56
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,520
Aren't I here?

57
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,280
I love you.

58
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,920
But the long distance is a real problem.

59
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:57,290
Fine.

60
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:58,570
Then tell me.

61
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,300
How do you want to solve it?

62
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,640
I don't know what to do either.

63
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,960
Let's just play it by ear.

64
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,120
Play it by ear?

65
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:07,480
Are you really going to be this irresponsible?

66
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,340
How am I being irresponsible?

67
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,920
I don't think you ever wanted to return to Xinjiang for me.

68
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,280
You don't love me at all.

69
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,200
You...

70
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:17,850
Stop saying I don't love you over every little thing.

71
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:32,200
Xuanqing.

72
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,440
You again.

73
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,360
Queen Mother.

74
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,600
The 99th reincarnation

75
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,040
is about to succeed.

76
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,490
Sinian's memory is slowly returning.

77
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:57,960
Are Sinian and I

78
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,960
doomed to a bad end?

79
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,880
Si-Sinian.

80
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,360
Xuanqing,

81
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:23,320
where did you hide Lu Sinian?

82
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:46,100
Sinian.

83
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:49,480
Sinian.

84
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,280
Sinian.

85
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:58,840
Xuanqing,

86
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:02,240
what exactly did you do to Lu Sinian?

87
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:06,720
He has reincarnated 99 times.

88
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:08,700
I was afraid he'd be too tired,

89
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,180
so I just let him sleep for a while.

90
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,480
Xuanqing,

91
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:28,560
how could you use such a vicious formation?

92
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,240
Vicious?

93
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,720
Our Flood Dragon Snake clan

94
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:41,280
has been suppressed by the Sea-Calming Needle for thousands of years.

95
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,560
You call me vicious,

96
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:45,240
but when have you ever not been vicious?

97
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,760
Stop arguing.

98
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:54,000
That's because you deserved it.

99
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,160
Unforgivable.
